  "content": "<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\">#writing #journalism</p>\n<h1 class=\"prose-sm text-4xl font-bold mb-6 mt-8 max-w-prose lg:pr-12 animate-on-scroll slide-from-left\" id=\"metadata\">Metadata</h1>\n<ul class=\"prose-sm list-disc list-outside ml-6 mb-4 space-y-2 max-w-prose\">\n<li class=\"prose-sm max-w-prose\">\n<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\">Author: <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/Mark-Kramer/e/B001IOBI9O/ref=dp_byline_cont_ebooks_1\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group prose-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-colors duration-200\">Mark Kramer and Wendy Call</a></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"prose-sm max-w-prose\">\n<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\">ASIN: B000SEH1KK</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"prose-sm max-w-prose\">\n<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\">Reference: <a href=\"https://www.amazon.com/dp/B000SEH1KK\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"external-link group prose-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-colors duration-200\">https://www.amazon.com/dp/B000SEH1KK</a></p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"prose-sm max-w-prose\">\n<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\"><a href=\"kindle://book?action=open&#x26;asin=B000SEH1KK\" class=\"prose-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-colors duration-200\">Kindle link</a></p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<h1 class=\"prose-sm text-4xl font-bold mb-6 mt-8 max-w-prose lg:pr-12 animate-on-scroll slide-from-left\" id=\"highlights\">Highlights</h1>\n<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\">Taking an idea, a central point, and pursuing it, turning it into a story that tells something about the way we live today, is the essence of narrative journalism. — location: <a href=\"kindle://book?action=open&#x26;asin=B000SEH1KK&#x26;location=344\" class=\"prose-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-colors duration-200\">344</a> ^ref-60575</p>\n<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>\n<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\">You don’t “hype up” in the wake of tragedy. You underwrite, letting the events speak for themselves. — location: <a href=\"kindle://book?action=open&#x26;asin=B000SEH1KK&#x26;location=355\" class=\"prose-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-colors duration-200\">355</a> ^ref-7657</p>\n<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>\n<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\">When you find a reporter whose work you admire, break his or her code. Examine the story and figure out what the reporter did, where he or she went, how that reporter constructed the story, and why it worked. — location: <a href=\"kindle://book?action=open&#x26;asin=B000SEH1KK&#x26;location=386\" class=\"prose-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-colors duration-200\">386</a> ^ref-21443</p>\n<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>\n<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\">It is just as unsatisfactory to constantly underrate yourself as it is to give yourself too much credit. — location: <a href=\"kindle://book?action=open&#x26;asin=B000SEH1KK&#x26;location=1698\" class=\"prose-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-colors duration-200\">1698</a> ^ref-26442</p>\n<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>\n<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\">Thinking too much about the present will lead you to ask the wrong questions about the past. Take the past on its own terms, not on ours. — location: <a href=\"kindle://book?action=open&#x26;asin=B000SEH1KK&#x26;location=1830\" class=\"prose-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-colors duration-200\">1830</a> ^ref-20013</p>\n<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>\n<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\">You need to provide readers two things in this sort of journalism: a detailed picture of the social setting and at least some insight into the psychology of the principals. I think of the setting as a horizontal plane and the individual as a vertical plane. The line created by their intersection—there lies the story. — location: <a href=\"kindle://book?action=open&#x26;asin=B000SEH1KK&#x26;location=3070\" class=\"prose-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-colors duration-200\">3070</a> ^ref-46601</p>\n<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>\n<p class=\"prose-p prose-sm max-w-prose mb-4 leading-relaxed dark:prose-invert animate-on-scroll\" style=\"max-width: 60ch;\">I write in the first person a lot. The “I” in my stories is the reader’s proxy. My great ambition is to take readers out of their comfort zones and put them in positions of discomfort. I want them to see and smell and taste and touch and hear the things that I did in their place as the reporter. — location: <a href=\"kindle://book?action=open&#x26;asin=B000SEH1KK&#x26;location=3184\" class=\"prose-sm text-blue-600 dark:text-blue-400 hover:underline transition-colors duration-200\">3184</a> ^ref-58294</p>\n<svg class=\"mx-auto my-8 w-full max-w-prose\" height=\"1\">\n  <line x1=\"0\" y1=\"0\" x2=\"100%\" y2=\"0\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1\" stroke-dasharray=\"2,4\" />\n</svg>",
